results.name: Minimal multiples from A016089 of primes from A129729.
comment: A016089 lists numbers n such that n divide n-th Lucas number A000032(n) while A129729 lists all possible prime divisors of elements of A016089 in the increasing order. This sequence lists minimal multiples from A016089 of primes from A129729.
results.author: _Max Alekseyev_, May 16 2008
